title: JUN 20 2022 - MASS SHOOTING AT JUNETEENTH CONCERT IN DC
description:
Over the weekend a mass shooting occurred in Washington DC at a Juneteenth Concert. Reports indicate one teenager was killed, and several, including a police officer, were wounded. According to surfacing surveillance, Uvalde Police did not even attempt to open the classroom door where children were being massacred. FINA, the administrators of international water sports competitions, have released new rules banning biological men from competing in women's sport events.  Jack Posobiec breaks down huge emerging news – Russia has now conducted several military operations against US-backed fighters in Syria at an American Outpost.  


Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
